            <title><![CDATA[Climate change and flying: what share of global CO2 emissions come from aviation?]]></title>
            <id>https://ourworldindata.org/co2-emissions-from-aviation</id>
            <link rel="alternate" href="https://ourworldindata.org/co2-emissions-from-aviation"/>
            <published>2020-10-22T11:00:00.000Z</published>
            <updated>2020-10-22T17:39:15.000Z</updated>
            <author><name>Hannah Ritchie</name></author>
            <summary><![CDATA[Flying is a highly controversial topic in climate debates. It accounts for around 2.5% of global CO2 emissions, but 3.5% when we take non-CO2 impacts on climate into account.<br><br><a href="https://ourworldindata.org/co2-emissions-from-aviation" target="_blank"><img src="https://ourworldindata.org/app/uploads/2020/10/Global-CO2-emissions-from-aviation-768x610.png"/></a>]]></summary>
            </entry>
